---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Case studies · SuiteHub" description="QS Express, Clean Factory, KM Seguridad and CVE Panamá: SMBs in Panama that multiplied their operational capacity with SuiteHub. Live clients today in Panama; soft launch in USA, Venezuela and Spain during 2026.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-[400px] bg-radial-brand pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="wrap relative pt-12 pb-16">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <span class="eyebrow">Case studies</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-bold leading-[1.05]">
          Businesses <span class="text-gradient">growing</span> with SuiteHub.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">
          Measurable results, not marketing. These are real numbers after implementation. All our live clients today are in <strong class="text-white">Panama</strong>; USA, Venezuela, and Spain enter <strong class="text-white">soft launch during 2026</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- QS Express full case -->
  <section id="qs-express" class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <article class="card-glass overflow-hidden">
        <header class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-0 border-b border-white/10">
          <div class="lg:col-span-3 p-10 lg:p-12">
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-400 font-semibold mb-4">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i> Featured case · Workshop vertical
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-4">
              QS Express tripled their <span class="text-gradient">operational capacity</span> in 4 weeks
            </h2>
            <p class="text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">
              Independent auto-repair shop in La Chorrera with 20+ years of experience, specialized in diesel systems.
              They migrated from Excel + notebooks to HUB Workshop (Pro Edition) and completely redesigned their intake,
              diagnosis and delivery flow.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-800 to-navy-900 p-10 flex items-center justify-center border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-white/5">
            <div class="text-center">
              <img src="/images/tallerqsexpress.png" alt="QS Express" class="w-32 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 p-3" />
              <div class="text-base font-display font-semibold">QS Express</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-ink-400 mt-1">La Chorrera, Western Panama</div>
              <a href="https://tallerqsexpress.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                 class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-3 text-xs text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300">
                tallerqsexpress.com <i class="fa-solid fa-external-link text-[10px]"></i>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 divide-x divide-y lg:divide-y-0 divide-white/5">
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-400">3×</div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-400 mt-2">More orders/day</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-400">0</div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-400 mt-2">DGI rejections</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-400">4 wks</div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-400 mt-2">To full speed</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-400">+40%</div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-400 mt-2">Revenue vs. previous quarter</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-10 lg:p-12 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-rose-400 font-semibold mb-3">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-xmark"></i> Before
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-ink-300">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Orders in notebooks, copies in Word</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> No traceability of which customer brought which vehicle</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Manual quotes via WhatsApp, no follow-up</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Invoicing on paper pads, no electronic DGI</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Parts inventory eyeballed</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Appointments forgotten or double-booked</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400 font-semibold mb-3">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> After SuiteHub
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-ink-300">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Intake in 30 seconds: plate → customer → complaint</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Every vehicle has a full service history</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Quotes as professional PDFs, shareable link</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> DGI electronic invoicing with official CUFE</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Real-time inventory with low-stock alerts</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Online booking: customer reserves, system confirms</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-600/10 via-brand-500/5 to-transparent p-10 lg:p-12 border-t border-white/5">
          <div class="text-brand-400 text-3xl mb-3">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left"></i>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-display italic text-ink-100 leading-relaxed mb-5">
            "Within a week we were already issuing electronic invoices with zero DGI rejections.
            What I loved most: the SuiteHub team didn't ask us to change how we work — they adapted
            the platform to our flow, not the other way around."
          </blockquote>
          <footer class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <img src="/images/tallerqsexpress.png" alt="QS Express" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/10 p-1" />
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">Raúl Romero</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-ink-400">Lead Technician — QS Express</div>
            </div>
          </footer>
        </div>

        <div class="p-10 lg:p-12 border-t border-white/5">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-400 font-semibold mb-4">
            SuiteHub stack used
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-crown text-brand-400"></i> Pro Edition
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-screwdriver-wrench text-brand-400"></i> HUB Workshop
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-receipt text-brand-400"></i> PAC Digifact
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen text-brand-400"></i> Installable PWA
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Clean Factory full case -->
  <section id="clean-factory" class="section bg-navy-900/30">
    <div class="wrap">
      <article class="card-glass overflow-hidden">
        <header class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-0 border-b border-white/10">
          <div class="lg:col-span-3 p-10 lg:p-12">
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-400 font-semibold mb-4">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-soap"></i> Real case · Laundry vertical
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-4">
              Clean Factory digitized their <span class="text-gradient">sneaker cleaning laundry</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">
              Laundry specialized in <strong class="text-white">professional sneaker cleaning</strong> in Panama.
              They migrated from notebooks and paper pads to a system with digital orders, PIN-based time clock,
              electronic invoicing with The Factory HKA and a public delivery form connected to the backend.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-800 to-navy-900 p-10 flex items-center justify-center border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-white/5">
            <div class="text-center">
              <img src="/images/cleanfactory.png" alt="Clean Factory" class="w-32 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-2xl bg-white p-3" />
              <div class="text-base font-display font-semibold">Clean Factory</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-ink-400 mt-1">Shoe Cleaning · Panama</div>
              <div class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-emerald-400 bg-emerald-400/10 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
                In production
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 divide-x divide-y lg:divide-y-0 divide-white/5">
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-400">0</div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-400 mt-2">DGI rejections</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-400">100%</div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-400 mt-2">Digital orders</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-400">PIN</div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-400 mt-2">Staff time clock</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-400">24/7</div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-400 mt-2">Online delivery</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-10 lg:p-12 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-rose-400 font-semibold mb-3">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-xmark"></i> Before
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-ink-300">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Orders in notebooks, no process status</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Invoicing on paper pads, no DGI</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Staff attendance on paper sheets</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Delivery orders via manual WhatsApp</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Month-end close done by hand</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400 font-semibold mb-3">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> After SuiteHub
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-ink-300">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Order with status timeline (received → washed → dried → ready)</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Electronic invoicing with HKA, official CUFE</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> PIN time clock with CSV payroll export</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Public delivery form → webhook into the system</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> 80mm thermal receipts at the counter, live dashboards</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-10 lg:p-12 border-t border-white/5">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-400 font-semibold mb-4">
            SuiteHub stack used
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt text-brand-400"></i> Core Edition
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-soap text-brand-400"></i> HUB Laundry
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-receipt text-brand-400"></i> PAC The Factory HKA
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-fingerprint text-brand-400"></i> PIN time clock
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-print text-brand-400"></i> 80mm thermal receipt
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- KM Seguridad full case -->
  <section id="km-seguridad" class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <article class="card-glass overflow-hidden">
        <header class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-0 border-b border-white/10">
          <div class="lg:col-span-3 p-10 lg:p-12">
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-400 font-semibold mb-4">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i> Real case · Security services
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-4">
              KM Seguridad unified <span class="text-gradient">five service lines</span> in a single platform
            </h2>
            <p class="text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">
              Panamanian company specialized in <strong class="text-white">alarms, CCTV, monitoring, equipment installation
              and electric fencing</strong>. They moved from spreadsheets and notebooks to HUB Core, centralizing contracts,
              technical history per customer, maintenance scheduling and DGI electronic invoicing in a single system.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-800 to-navy-900 p-10 flex items-center justify-center border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-white/5">
            <div class="text-center">
              <img src="/images/kmslogo.jpeg" alt="KM Seguridad" class="w-32 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-2xl bg-white p-3" />
              <div class="text-base font-display font-semibold">KM Seguridad</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-ink-400 mt-1">La Chorrera, Western Panama</div>
              <div class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-emerald-400 bg-emerald-400/10 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
                In production
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 divide-x divide-y lg:divide-y-0 divide-white/5">
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-400">5</div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-400 mt-2">Service lines</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-400">0</div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-400 mt-2">DGI rejections</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-400">24/7</div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-400 mt-2">Active monitoring</div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-400">1</div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-400 mt-2">System, not five</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-10 lg:p-12 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-rose-400 font-semibold mb-3">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-xmark"></i> Before
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-ink-300">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Five service lines tracked across separate Excel spreadsheets</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Paper notebooks for technical visits and installations</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> No unified record of what each customer had installed</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Pre-printed invoice books, no electronic DGI invoicing</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Preventive maintenance forgotten or notified late</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-minus text-rose-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Manual collections, no per-customer balance view</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400 font-semibold mb-3">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> After SuiteHub
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-ink-300">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> One system for alarms, CCTV, monitoring, installation and electric fencing</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Customer profile with all installed equipment and its history</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> PDF quotes with one-click conversion to invoice</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> DGI electronic invoicing with official CUFE</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Equipment and parts inventory with low-stock alerts</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400 mt-1.5 text-xs"></i> Receivables with per-customer balances and aging</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-10 lg:p-12 border-t border-white/5">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-400 font-semibold mb-4">
            SuiteHub stack used
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt text-brand-400"></i> Core Edition
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-cube text-brand-400"></i> HUB Core
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-receipt text-brand-400"></i> DGI electronic invoicing
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-boxes-stacked text-brand-400"></i> Multi-service inventory
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-sm">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-money-bill-wave text-brand-400"></i> Receivables
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CVE Panamá full case -->
  <section id="cve-panama" class="section bg-navy-900/30">
    <div class="wrap">
      <article class="card-glass overflow-hidden">
        <header class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-0 border-b border-white/10">
          <div class="lg:col-span-3 p-10 lg:p-12">
            <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-400 font-semibold mb-4">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-barcode"></i> Real case · Distribution &amp; technology
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-4">
              CVE Panamá centralized its <span class="text-gradient">identification &amp; barcode catalog</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-ink-300 leading-relaxed">
              B2B distributor of <strong class="text-white">identification and barcode technology</strong> in Panama:
              standard and custom labels, ribbon, toner, packing tape, personnel ID, barcode printers and scanners, and
              technical support. They serve retail, wholesale, manufacturing, transport and logistics. They migrated from
              spreadsheets to HUB Core, unifying catalog, inventory, B2B quotes and DGI electronic invoicing.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-800 to-navy-900 p-10 flex items-center justify-center border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-white/5">
            <div class="text-center">
              <img src="/images/cvepanama_web.webp" alt="CVE Panamá" class="w-44 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-2xl bg-white p-3" />
              <div class="text-base font-display font-semibold">CVE Panamá</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-ink-400 mt-1">Technology distribution · Panama</div>
              <div class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-emerald-400 bg-emerald-400/10 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
                Live in production
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </header>

